name: Marin Kitagawa LoRA
description:
Hi! This is the first LoRA model I've created of Marin Kitagawa from "My dress up darling" anime show series.

The training set mainly contains her face, but also iconic outfits like school uniform and her black bikini with yellow petals.
The set was trained on Linaqruf's Kohya-ss LoRa Dreambooth Google Collab version, on Anything V3.1 model and anime VAE.

Main prompt for generation I would suggest to use is - "1girl, solo, Marin Kitagawa".

The model is capable of generating NSFW arts, but the weights should be around :0.6 - :0.8 and prompt box should contain "nsfw" for it to work.

The model is capable of generating custom outfits with Kitagawa's face.

If you would like to generate custom outfits, I would suggest to put the weight at :0.5 - :0.7.
If you would like to get her face a little bit more detailed, I suggest you use weights of :0.7 - :0.8., but feel free to play around with the weights yourself :3

The model tends to create her iconic "peace hand sign", but this could be fixed in inpainting easily.

modelVersions.name: V1.2a
modelVersions.description:
Swapped out bad pictures from training set that gave "blurry" images in output.
On request - added a few more NSFW pictures, but they should be prompted to work, so model still mainly outputs SFW.
Increased "Marin Kitagawa" token strength, so it should be more prominent.
If you encounter any bugs or glitches in the output images, please report them in discussion thread of this model.
Thank You :3
